articles.title: Most homebuyers now need six-figure income to achieve the 'American dream' - Yahoo Finance
articles.description: The median income of the US homebuyer jumped 21.6% to $107,000 from $88,000 during the period of NAR’s 2023 report.
articles.content:
More first-time homebuyers returned to the market in the last year, but they had to come with bigger wads of cash.
